body_html:
It looks like the nasm website is totally down for the count. Still.

The good news is that, at HEAD, this isn't a problem because we have the redundant GCS mirror URL. However I've got two PRs out to fix it anyway at HEAD and in the r0.12 branch. Earlier release branches do not need to be fixed because ≤r0.11 don't build nasm.

Thank you for bringing this to our attention.
